oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Muster roll fragment of the 25th Tenn. Inf. Regt., CSA.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This is a fragment of the muster roll of the 25th Tenn. Inf. Regt., CSA. Names listed include Capt. R. Donaldson, Lt. James Riley, Lt. J.K. P. Davis, Lt. W.H. Chilton, Lt. James Garrett, Adjt. J.C. Chowning,; Quartermaster W.S. Davis, Commissary A. J. Stephens, and Surgeon W.G. Brown. The home towns of the officers include Snake Point, Tenn., Fox Springs, Tenn., and Celina, Tenn.
